<HL>
   Supreme Court
   Hardens Stance
   On Pricing Suits
   ---
   Ruling Makes It Difficult
   To Sue Manufacturers
   That Cap Retail Prices
   ----
   By Stephen Wermiel
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
05/15/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A3
</SO>
